{
  "stem": "18258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 330.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I understand.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The First World War.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have very few impressions from then, except I knew my dad was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came home a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was in hospital, he was wounded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we struggled in our store, which was run by Mother, very efficiently.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I really had very-- I suffered very little.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember one incident when mother got a hold of half a kilo of lump sugar, which was a rarity.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I-- I rationed it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had one lump every day after my mid-- my mid-day meal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it lasted a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that is just typical, because we had no sweets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- In 1918, I remember when the masses of people flocked into the inner city when the Republic was declared, when it became known that Kaiser Francis-- Kaiser Karl had abdicated.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for a while, everything was all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have more experiences with my religion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I also remember-- I have to backtrack-- I remember the funeral procession of Kaiser Francis Joseph, who passed the main artery in Vienna, Mariahilfer Strasse.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were invited to people who had a window facing out, and we saw the cortege going from Schonbrunn, the summer palace, where the kaiser died, to the inner city, to the [GERMAN], where he were-- was then laid out and seen for display.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's one of the impressions I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I was not affected, not interested, until about, I would say, until I was about 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, my mother, who was a very good piano player, took me to my first concert, in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is the biggest and best-known venue in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
